The paper proposes a novel multi-fidelity framework that combines Gaussian Processes and deep neural networks to handle discontinuous cross-correlations among systems with different levels of fidelity. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE), Systems and Control (cs.SY), or Software Engineering (cs.SE) sub-categories.
